      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield strength, and tangent modulus were characterized from tensile coupons machined from the same material lot as the tested constructs. Geometric dimensions were measured by CMM on each of the 11 constructs. Uncertainty in material properties was propagated through Monte Carlo sampling (500 runs) to bound QoI variability. No sensitivity analysis linking specific input parameters to QoI variance has been formally conducted; such analysis is planned for a subsequent revision to identify dominant drivers. Gradation 3 achieved for input characterization."
