      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement were compared using the E/uval validation metric incorporating experimental uncertainty (uval) and model prediction error (E). All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10%. Gradation 3 achieved."
